TextBlock.Text: BOBER: Oh my god that took a lot of work... But we're here. The sun of this system is red and bright, and this moon is drenched.
BILLY: Come on Bober, you know why we're here. Let's get moving!
KATHERYNE: Haha! I found the engraving first- and oop-
KATHERYNE: The engraving appears to be the start of a new coordinate. It goes from top right to bottom left, and oddly enough, to the bottom right.
BOBER: Gah... This is getting boring.
BILLY: Shut up, Bober. No wonder you were named that. You are such a child.
KATHERYNE: Alright, we all know how this goes. The secondary engraving is of that planet filled with the symbol that looks like A.
